VLIB_HAARDETOBJ_sObjectList Struct Reference

#include <VLIB_haarDetectObjects_types.h>

Detailed Description

This structure holds object list information.

Parameters:
numObjects Total number of objects
objectPos Pointer to the buffer where numObjects number of object information is stored. Each object information is defined as packed format of its 'Y' & 'X' co-ordinate. Upper 16 bit is the 'Y' co-ordinate, lower 16 bit is 'X' co-ordinate.
